Aldi Increases Price of Milk on Global Dairy Demand, DPA Says

-- B y   B r i a n   P a r k i n
-- 
2011-05-02T19:50:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-02/aldi-increases-price-of-milk-on-global-dairy-demand-dpa-says.html
Discount food retailer Aldi Group will
increase the price of milk in  Germany  amid rising global demand
for dairy produce, the Deutsche Presse-Agentur newswire
reported, without citing a source for the information.  Aldi will increase the retail price of one liter cartons of
milk by 4 cents or 8 percent, DPA said.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Brian Parkin in Berlin at 
 bparkin@bloomberg.net ;  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Hertling at   jhertling@bloomberg.net  